          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“I have pursued my enemies and destroyed them; Neither did I turn back again till they were destroyed. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "“I have pursued my enemies and destroyed them; Neither did I turn back again till they were destroyed."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And I have destroyed them and wounded them, So that they could not rise; They have fallen under my feet. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And I have destroyed them and wounded them, So that they could not rise; They have fallen under my feet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And I have destroyed them and wounded them, So that they could not rise; They have fallen under my feet."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For You have armed me with strength for the battle; You have subdued under me those who rose against me. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For You have armed me with strength for the battle; You have subdued under me those who rose against me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "You have also given me the necks of my enemies, So that I destroyed those who hated me. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "You have also given me the necks of my enemies, So that I destroyed those who hated me."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 42,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They looked, but there  was none to save; Even  to the Lord, but He did not answer them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 42,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They looked, but there  was none to save; Even  to the Lord, but He did not answer them."
